parameters: Oh, how beautiful... your body is...

I serve Lady Dorothea, the master of Blood Moon
Castle.
What the hell is going on?!
Do you think you can defeat me?en(v[263]>=100)

To come this far and defy me with a blade...!
Unforgivable.
It's useless to run away! And... who are you?!

Oh, \v[111]-san... You haven't forgotten about
that incident, have you...?
Ugh... Of course... I haven't... forgotten...

Ugh... Fine... I'll pretend I didn't see anything
here... Just go away quickly...

\v[111], you came all over my body, didn't you?
Don't you want to do that pleasurable thing again?
Ugh... Of course... I haven't... forgotten...

Ugh... I have no choice... I'll pretend I didn't
see anything here... Just go away quickly...

I wonder if I was broken by the enemy... How
troublesome...

I want to visit Rein Garnet and try out a fun game
that's popular, right? A card game.
Oh no~ What are you doing?

It seems that those who try to forcefully cross
the Flame Zone are immediately engulfed in flames
of hellfire. It's quite scary, isn't it?

Frya was a witch who took care of me in the past,
and I've always wanted to repay her kindness. I'm
thinking of giving her a scroll that contains a
certain forbidden spell.

It's super risky, you know~. So, it's difficult
for someone like me to bring it along. But I know
where it is, so if you happen to meet her, please
let her know.
I'm a bit busy right now

Well, it doesn't really matter, but (couldn't you
just tell her yourself?)
I'm a little busy right now...
Oh no~ What are you doing?

the Flame Zone are immediately engulfed in flames

No way, is this Marina...?! It can't be true...

Marina had been transformed into a doll,
reflecting the curse!

So this is what happens when you pick a fight with
a witch... but why...
I heard a rumor that Flyer died... No way...

Oh no! Even if you show me your body like that,
it's troubling, old man.

It's a closing sale~~! I'll make it cheap, so come
take a look~~
It seems like \C[2] won't let me in anymore today.

Oh my...! Did you get attacked by demons or
bandits?

I've heard that an incredibly powerful being is
sealed in the basement of the shrine. It's
probably best not to get too close.

I hope we can quickly achieve a peaceful world
without demons, magical girls. Let's work hard
together, shall we?

It's relatively safe in this town, but I wouldn't
recommend going out dressed like that too much.

In this tavern, research is conducted daily to
defeat demons and bandits, so if you're a magical
girl, you should join in too.

Oh my... you! This is no good... like that...!
Ahh, ahh, ahh...

Don't you think it's a wonderful city? I want to
protect it... Of course, Lady Dorothea too.

Even if my clothes are stripped away... I won't
lose my pride... That's what it means, right!

Goddess Althea, benevolent deity Badea, and
Lidim... It seems that there were various gods in
ancient times.
Hey, are you okay? Aren't you cold?

You're in the same line of work, huh? How about
your memory? I can't remember anything at all. But
I wonder what would happen if I did remember. It
seems like it would be confusing and I don't
really like that.

away the vines!
